Author: koilop_official
Title: ico
Body: Koilop is a decentralized peer-to-peer freelance system, in which buyers/clients and freelancers/service providers can conduct business and exchange of money for service using non-bounded smart contracts by reputation and cash in escrow. We intend to combine economic initiative with reputation into one by tokenizing reputation and assigning it a value. Thus, all parties, moderators included (if need be), have a common goal to act honestly since, since they all have a common interest — which is to exchange services and monies.  We will completely revolutionize the current digital marketplace by developing our Koilop model ecosystem with a full integration of the blockchain technology.      Facebook: https://facebook.com/KoilopOfficial Twitter: https://twitter.com/KoilopOfficial Medium: https://medium.com/koilopofficial Telegram: https://t.me/koilopofficial Github: https://github.com/koiloplimited/smart-contract Youtube: https://youtube.com/channel/UCvRMaMXD3yzEAu8ERBvxIGw?view_as=subscriber Contact us: contact@koilopecosystem.com
